===Battle of the Network Stars (2017)===
For this edition, rather than the standard network vs. network format, fielding of the teams is based on the TV characters attributed to each celebrity—cops vs. TV sitcoms, White House vs. lawyers, TV moms &amp; dads vs. TV kids, etc.
